Feature: Killing lines

  Scenario: Killing a comment
    Given I clear the buffer
    When I insert:
    """
    //function foo() {
    //    bar();
    //}
    """
    And I turn on js2-mode and js2-refactor-mode
    And I go to the front of the word "function"
    And I press "C-c C-m k"
    Then I should see:
    """
    //
    //    bar();
    //}
    """

